                <note rend="inline" type="source">840.48 Refugees/1074: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-12-12T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 12, 1938—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>770. For Rublee. Your 1416, December 9, 4 p.m. Warren has communicated direct
                    with Rothschild. In connection with preliminary studies, please advise
                    specifically what part of British Guiana the 40,000 square miles comprises. Is
                    the figure of 40,000 confidential?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
